<br>
Since your eventually going to end up with your max anyway, does it matter if you deceide to put your points all into INT or CHA? Or would you want em in STA for... hp when your dead... or something along thoes lines.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I'd say put all points into stamina... the sooner you can max stamina the sooner you can work on HP gear.  When you are on a raid you will have your stamina maxed by shamans usually thats why HP gear is better than stamina gear once you have sufficent stamina.  Left over points I would suggest strength.<br>
<br>
Why warriors are fun?... to me it's the control.  You tend to be the &quot;leader&quot; of the group as the warrior. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Froglok Champion<br>
